text: Jaroslav Hatla (born 5 May 1973) is a Czech equestrian. He competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Czech Republic Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hořice (Jičín District)
